      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/card/10_1186_1471_2105_6_225__task_002/scope_drift",
      "@type": "asbval:ScopeDriftAssertion",
      "asbval:drift_notes": [
        "The card focuses narrowly on the PLAGE decomposition component and its mathematical conversion of intensity matrices to activity scores. The paper's scope is broader\u2014it presents PALS as a comprehensive system for metabolite set enrichment analysis, comparing mPLAGE against ORA and GSEA, and demonstrating applications to pathways, molecular families, and Mass2Motifs. The card's framing is a valid sub-task within the paper's scope but represents only one component of the larger work."
      ],
      "asbval:n_drift_notes": 1,
