    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/card/10_1186_1471_2105_6_225__task_005/scope_drift",
      "@type": "asbval:ScopeDriftAssertion",
      "asbval:drift_notes": [
        "The research question proposes extending PALS to support user-uploaded custom metabolite sets via an API, which is a future capability not described in the paper. The paper demonstrates that PALS already has modular support for user-defined metabolite sets in principle, but does not address the specific proposal of accepting user-uploaded custom collections through PALS Viewer.",
        "The card frames this as a research question about extending functionality, but the paper is a completed study describing PALS as already implemented with support for pathways, Molecular Families, and Mass2Motifs. No API extension or user-upload feature is mentioned."
      ],
      "asbval:n_drift_notes": 2,
      "asbval:target_artifact_id": "task_005",
      "asbval:target_artifact_kind": "card",
      "prov:wasAttributedTo": "anthropic/claude-haiku-4-5-20251001",
