    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/comparative-enrichment-method-evaluation/006",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "PALS is freely available at https://pals.glasgowcompbio.org/ (accessed on 5 February 2021)... These alternative methods, used for benchmarking experiments, are included in the PALS Python library",
      "asbval:note": "ORA and GSEA are implemented within the PALS library, not as separate repositories. The card lists the PALS repo for ORA, which is technically correct (ORA is part of PALS) but misleading\u2014ORA is not a standalone tool with its own repo.",
