      "asbval:target_claim_text": "Extend PALS pathway activity scoring to user-defined metabolite set collections (beyond built-in pathways, Molecular Families, and Mass2Motifs) by validating user-uploaded sets and dispatching them through the PLAGE decomposition pipeline.",
