      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/metabolite-set-analysis/013",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "To anaylse Mass2Motifs, a data set from the GNPS-MS2LDA workflow, consisting of 70 Rhamnacea species from two clades and various genera, was used [4]... To analyse both MFs and Mass2Motifs, Python code is provided in PALS to retrieve information on the metabolite sets as well as the peak intensity table from GNPS (Figure 7B).",
      "asbval:note": "Semantic equivalence: MS2LDA provides Mass2Motif data that PALS can analyze.",
