      }
    },
    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/metabolite-set-decomposition-plage/003",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "PALS also presents a comprehensive Python-based library that can be easily run in several modes: as a standalone tool, an interactive Web application (PALS Viewer), or a Python library.",
