      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "As input to activity level decomposition using mPLAGE... a peak intensity matrix X is constructed for each metabolite set, defined here as a collection of features that have been grouped in some manner, e.g., forming a particular metabolic pathway or molecular family.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper describes input requirements for PALS/mPLAGE including peak intensity matrices and metabolite groupings.",
