      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "PALS is designed to look at how metabolic pathways or other groups of metabolites change between different experimental conditions... The results demonstrated that the mPLAGE method is robust to noise and missing values, which is particularly important for metabolomics data.",
