      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/molecular-family-grouping-analysis/006",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "For the MF analysis, Global Natural Products Social Molecular Networking (GNPS) example data were taken from the American Gut Project.",
