      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "Features are annotated as compound formulae and these are linked to the metabolites in the metabolite set/pathway of interest.",
      "asbval:note": "Annotation requirement confirmed. Paper also notes: 'After processing in PiMP, the complete Plasma and CSF data produced 15,584 and 8154 features, of which 1647 and 1132 had associated metabolite annotations, respectively,' demonstrating that unannotated features are not used in pathway analysis.",
