    {
      "@id": "asbval:assertion/skill/rank-order-correlation-analysis/005",
      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "PALS can be run either as a standalone tool, imported as a Python library, or used via a Web interface allowing users with a wide range of expertise and requirements to use it... To assist beginners, a Web interface is provided to run PALS in an intuitive and user-friendly manner.",
      "asbval:note": "Paper confirms a web interface exists for PALS but does not explicitly name it 'PALS Viewer' in the provided passages. The web interface is described as available for running PALS and visualizing results, but specific mention of 'PALS Viewer' as a distinct product name is not found in the passages. The functional role (interactive visualization) is supported.",
