      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The main algorithm in PALS is based on the pathway level analysis of gene expression (PLAGE) factorisation method and is denoted as mPLAGE (PLAGE for metabolomics)... Our adaptation of the PLAGE method, denoted as mPLAGE (PLAGE for metabolomics), was independently implemented in Python for use in metabolomics.",
      "asbval:note": "PALS implements mPLAGE, which is the PLAGE method adapted for metabolomics.",
